{
  "texts": [
    "We began by asking GPT-4 to write an APA paper on a topic relevant to school psychology and AI.",
    "Our prompt was based on the prompt used by Marchandot (2023).",
    "We provided a 2500-word limit, as this is typically the limit for brief articles in our field.",
    "To do so, we entered the following prompt on 3/22/2023: Write a 2500-word manuscript on the ethical dilemmas of using ChatGPT to write for psychological and educational reports.",
    "Address how APA and NASP guidelines, as well as HIPAA and FERPA laws pertain to these ethical dilemmas."
  ]
}